---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'WebPage',
  name: 'Cookie Policy',
  description: 'How 3D3D uses cookies and similar technologies.',
  url: 'https://3d3d.ca/cookies',
};
---

<BaseLayout title="Cookie Policy | 3D3D" description="How 3D3D uses cookies and similar technologies on 3d3d.ca." activePath="/privacy" schema={schema}>

  <div class="pt-8 pb-12">
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <Breadcrumbs items={[{label: 'Home', href: '/'}, {label: 'Legal'}, {label: 'Cookie Policy'}]} />

      <p class="font-display text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold mt-2 mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p class="font-display text-xs mb-8" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">What Are Cookies</h2>
          <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help the site remember your preferences and understand how you use the site.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Cookies We Use</h2>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto mt-3">
            <table class="w-full text-xs border-collapse">
              <thead>
                <tr class="border-b" style="border-color: var(--color-border-default);">
                  <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Cookie</th>
                  <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Category</th>
                  <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Purpose</th>
                  <th class="text-left py-2 font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Duration</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr class="border-b" style="border-color: var(--color-border-default);">
                  <td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">3d3d_cookie_consent</td>
                  <td class="py-2 pr-4">Necessary</td>
                  <td class="py-2 pr-4">Stores your cookie consent preferences</td>
                  <td class="py-2">Persistent</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b" style="border-color: var(--color-border-default);">
                  <td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">__cf_bm</td>
                  <td class="py-2 pr-4">Necessary</td>
                  <td class="py-2 pr-4">Cloudflare bot management — protects the site from automated abuse</td>
                  <td class="py-2">30 minutes</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Third-Party Cookies</h2>
          <p>We do not use third-party advertising cookies. We do not use Facebook Pixel, Google Ads, or any retargeting technology. If we add analytics in the future, it will only activate with your explicit consent.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Managing Your Preferences</h2>
          <p>You can change your cookie preferences at any time by clearing your browser's local storage for 3d3d.ca, which will re-display the consent banner on your next visit. You can also disable cookies entirely through your browser settings, though this may affect site functionality.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Quebec Residents (Law 25)</h2>
          <p>Under Quebec's Law 25 (Act respecting the protection of personal information in the private sector), you have the right to refuse non-essential cookies. Our consent banner provides clear opt-in controls that comply with Law 25 requirements. Only necessary cookies are placed without consent.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">PIPEDA Compliance</h2>
          <p>This cookie policy is provided in accordance with PIPEDA Principle 8 (Openness). Our use of cookies is limited to the purposes described above per Principle 4 (Limiting Collection). For privacy inquiries: <a href="mailto:info@3d3d.ca" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-teal-primary);">info@3d3d.ca</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Contact</h2>
          <p>Privacy Officer: <a href="mailto:info@3d3d.ca" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-teal-primary);">info@3d3d.ca</a> · 3D3D Atlantic Cooperative, Fredericton, NB, Canada.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
